title: Ministry of Majority Welfare Development (Maharashtra)
text:
The Ministry of Majority Welfare Development is a Ministry of the <a href="Government%20of%20Maharashtra">Government of Maharashtra</a>. 
state. 
The Ministry is headed by a <a href="Cabinet%20%28government%29">cabinet level</a> Minister. <a href="Vijay%20Namdevrao%20Wadettiwar">Vijay Namdevrao Wadettiwar</a> is Current Minister of Majority Welfare Development <a href="Government%20of%20Maharashtra">Government of Maharashtra</a>.
